&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( also known by the spelling nandi ) is a 2002 kannada action-drama film directed by d. rajendra babu featuring sudeep , sindhu menon and radhika chaudhari in the lead roles . the film features background score and soundtrack composed by gurukiran and lyrics by kaviraj and v. nagendra prasad . the film released on 27 december 2002